{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_03_02",
  "title": "miho",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（結局、mihoさんは祭典に出ないと言って譲らず）\n（祭典では昔の映像が使われることになった）",
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3333.3333334,
          "startTime": 8.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、いたいた、mihoさん\nちょうど探してたところだったんです",
      "startTime": 11.6666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.0000001271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……なんのご用でしょう",
      "startTime": 14.0000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "例の祭典の主催から\n当日流す映像を選定してくれと頼まれまして",
      "startTime": 17.7666668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんにも一緒に確認してもらった方が\nいいと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 23.566667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2000006993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、言っていただければ私がやっておくのに\n……いえ、それでは二度手間になりますね",
      "startTime": 29.0897723084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、手早くチェックしてしまいましょう",
      "startTime": 32.7666678746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 37.1500068027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、{user}さんと一緒に\n昔の映像を見ることになるとは思いませんでした",
      "startTime": 41.0666734694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今見てもやっぱり凄いですね\nさすがあの頃、トップクラスの人気だっただけあります",
      "startTime": 48.8333401361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、BIG4を育てた敏腕マネージャーさんは\n持ち上げるのがお上手ですね",
      "startTime": 56.6000068027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺の知り合いも、Sundanceは好きだったようで\n時々褒めてましたよ",
      "startTime": 61.7666724521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達を幸せにしたい気持ちが見えると\nそんなことを言ってました",
      "startTime": 67.3666724521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……へえ",
      "startTime": 69.400011889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "あの人は、敗者になんて目もくれないと思っていました\nそれとも勝者の余裕かしら",
      "startTime": 75.8666816074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "その知り合いって、長瀬麻奈のことでしょう\n下手なごまかし方をしなくても結構ですよ",
      "startTime": 82.5333482741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そういうつもりじゃ……",
      "startTime": 85.400015958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "Sundanceはそれだけいいグループだからこそ\nやっぱり祭典に出てほしいということをですね",
      "startTime": 90.600015958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……そう言っていただけるのは、ありがたいのですけど",
      "startTime": 93.700015958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "葉ちゃんがもういませんから\n二人一緒でないなら、祭典に出たって意味がありません",
      "startTime": 100.000015958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（数年前、Sundanceは絶頂期に活動休止した）\n（その理由は――）",
      "startTime": 108.7333472568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、活動休止の理由は公表されませんでしたよね？\n記事も目立たなくて、俺も後から気付いたくらいで",
      "startTime": 115.1666795729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "葉ちゃんが病気を公表したがらなかったんです\nあの時は、少し休んだらすぐ復帰するつもりでしたし",
      "startTime": 123.0333462396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "結局……それは叶いませんでしたけど",
      "startTime": 127.9666775384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（快復しないまま、葉さんはやがて病気で亡くなった）\n（――奇しくも、麻奈の事故のたった数日前に）",
      "startTime": 137.0333574293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "この頃は、麻奈も、葉さんもいなくなるとは\n思いもしませんでしたね……",
      "startTime": 144.9666968661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "取り残された私達が\n一緒に残業する羽目になるとも思いませんでしたけどね",
      "startTime": 149.0666958489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "確かに",
      "startTime": 152.8333696363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "それに……結末は変わらなくても、もう数日違ったら\n異なる未来があったかもしれません",
      "startTime": 160.3667060213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "あるいは、あの人の最期が少しだけ違ったら\nあんな――あんなに、強烈なものでなかったなら",
      "startTime": 167.8666958488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、{user}さんとだけは\n昔の話はしたくなかったです",
      "startTime": 176.4333401358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈は今でも大勢の人に大事にされていて\n今回だって、あの子達がせっせとカバーしてくれるのに",
      "startTime": 182.4000129059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "葉ちゃんのことは、誰も何も言わなくなっちゃった\n……あんなに、みんなに好かれていたのに",
      "startTime": 191.8666775381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（実際、亡くなった後の扱いは差があるかもしれない）",
      "startTime": 195.3000240957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（それは麻奈の事故が衝撃的だったのに対して）\n（葉さんがひっそり亡くなったのもあるんだろうが……）",
      "startTime": 203.233357429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、葉ちゃんは\nなんのためにずっと頑張ってきたっていうのよ",
      "startTime": 209.0000149404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（……もしかして）",
      "startTime": 211.9000057851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.4833391184
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.4833391184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、この祭典、I-UNITYに優勝して\nそして――長瀬麻奈を抹殺します",
      "startTime": 220.5000057851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 226.5666704172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "葉さんが忘れられつつあるから、麻奈もそうなれって？\nI-UNITYで言ってたのはそういう意味ですか？",
      "startTime": 232.499997647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、ただの逆恨みじゃないですか\n麻奈だって事故に遭いたくて遭った訳じゃないですよ！",
      "startTime": 239.699997647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね、逆恨みよ\n……分かってるわよ、そんなこと",
      "startTime": 246.7333381011,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3366.6796366999847,
          "startTime": 250.1000177378
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様です\n祭典に提出する映像のリスト、確認しておいて下さい",
      "startTime": 253.6000177378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、面倒なところをお願いしてしまって",
      "startTime": 257.733349291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、自分のステージは自分が一番覚えてますから",
      "startTime": 262.2666826243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk024.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、今スタジオで練習しているみたいですが\nあの曲は一体なんなんです？",
      "startTime": 271.0000383372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、祭典で歌う曲でしょう\nさくら達がまだスタジオに残って自主練してるみたいで",
      "startTime": 276.2000078196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk025.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことは分かってます\n祭典も近いのにこの出来はどうなのかと言ってるんです",
      "startTime": 281.8333838776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk026.m4a",
      "text": "怜がずっと音程を外してました\nでも芽衣が一番酷いですね、あれはただのカラオケです",
      "startTime": 288.366717211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、二人ともダンスの方が得意なので\nもしかしたら、そちらに気を取られてるのかも……",
      "startTime": 296.0333838776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh023.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、この曲もご存じなんですか？\n……その、麻奈がよくライブで歌ってた曲ですけど……",
      "startTime": 303.8333337147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk027.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょう\n昔、何度も聴いて研究しましたから",
      "startTime": 310.4000220612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-mhk028.m4a",
      "text": "だから下手くそに歌われると、余計腹が立ちます\nマネージャーならちゃんと本番までに対処して下さい",
      "startTime": 316.56672128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh024.m4a",
      "text": "（……この人、麻奈を嫌いなはずだよな？）\n（理由までは納得出来ないけど、それはそれとしてだ）",
      "startTime": 324.3000586823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_02-koh025.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん\n……今は、麻奈のことをどう思ってるんですか？",
      "startTime": 331.0000505443,
      "sfxList": []
